{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "bengkel-api-collection",
		"name": "Bengkel API",
		"description": "Koleksi Postman untuk Sistem Informasi Bengkel.\n\n## Cara Penggunaan\n1. **Variabel**: `base_url` → URL aplikasi (default: `http://localhost:8000`)\n2. **Auto-login**: Pre-request script akan otomatis login jika token kosong\n3. **Manual**: Jalankan **Login** dulu → token tersimpan otomatis ke variable `token`\n\n## Daftar Endpoint\n- **Auth**: Login, Logout\n- **User**: Get Authenticated User\n- **Customers**: Get All Customers\n- **Services**: Get All Services\n\n## Testing\nSetiap endpoint sudah dilengkapi test script (tab **Tests**) untuk memvalidasi response secara otomatis.\nJalankan dengan **Collection Runner** atau **Run All** untuk mengecek semua endpoint sekaligus.\n\n⚠️ Pastikan `base_url` sudah sesuai环境 (contoh: `http://localhost:8000` jika pakai `php artisan serve --port=8000`).",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"lastUpdated": "2026-07-20T13:30:00+07:00"
	},
	"event": [
		{
			"listen": "prerequest",
			"script": {
				"exec": [
					"// Auto-login jika token belum tersedia",
					"var token = pm.collectionVariables.get('token');",
					"var loginUrl = pm.collectionVariables.get('base_url') + '/api/login';",
					"",
					"if (!token || token === '') {",
					"    console.log('Token kosong, mencoba login otomatis...');",
					"    ",
					"    var loginRequest = {",
					"        url: loginUrl,",
					"        method: 'POST',",
					"        header: {",
					"            'Content-Type': 'application/json',",
					"            'Accept': 'application/json'",
					"        },",
					"        body: {",
					"            mode: 'raw',",
					"            raw: JSON.stringify({",
					"                email: 'admin@bengkel.test',",
					"                password: 'password'",
					"            })",
					"        }",
					"    };",
					"",
					"    pm.sendRequest(loginRequest, function (err, res) {",
					"        if (err) {",
					"            console.log('Gagal auto-login:', err);",
					"        } else {",
					"            try {",
					"                var json = res.json();",
					"                if (json.success && json.data && json.data.token) {",
					"                    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
					"                    console.log('Auto-login berhasil, token tersimpan.');",
					"                }",
					"            } catch(e) {",
					"                console.log('Gagal parse response auto-login:', e);",
					"            }",
					"        }",
					"    });",
					"}"
				],
				"type": "text/javascript"
			}
		}
	],
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:8000",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"description": "Endpoint untuk autentikasi menggunakan Laravel Sanctum.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code 200', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response format sukses', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('success', true);",
									"    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('message');",
									"    pm.expect(json.message).to.include('Login berhasil');",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Token dan data user tersedia', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('user');",
									"    pm.expect(json.data.user).to.have.all.keys('id', 'name', 'email', 'role', 'phone', 'email_verified_at', 'created_at', 'updated_at');",
									"    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('token');",
									"    pm.expect(json.data.token).to.match(/^\\d+\\|/);",
									"    pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('token_type', 'Bearer');",
									"});",
									"",
									"// Simpan token ke collection variable",
									"var json = pm.response.json();",
									"if (json.success && json.data && json.data.token) {",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
									"    console.log('Token berhasil disimpan:', json.data.token);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"admin@bengkel.test\",\n    \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/login",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Login untuk mendapatkan token Sanctum.\n\n**Response sukses:**\n```json\n{\n    \"success\": true,\n    \"message\": \"Login berhasil.\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"user\": { ... },\n        \"token\": \"1|abc123...\",\n        \"token_type\": \"Bearer\"\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Response gagal:**\n```json\n{\n    \"success\": false,\n    \"message\": \"Email atau password salah.\"\n}\n```"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Login Berhasil",
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"success\": true,\n    \"message\": \"Login berhasil.\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"user\": {\n            \"id\": 1,\n            \"name\": \"Admin Bengkel\",\n            \"email\": \"admin@bengkel.test\",\n            \"role\": \"admin\",\n            \"phone\": \"081234567890\",\n            \"email_verified_at\": null,\n            \"created_at\": \"2026-07-20T06:30:00.000000Z\",\n            \"updated_at\": \"2026-07-20T06:30:00.000000Z\"\n        },\n        \"token\": \"1|abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12\",\n        \"token_type\": \"Bearer\"\n    }\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "Login Gagal",
							"status": "Unauthorized",
							"code": 401,
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"success\": false,\n    \"message\": \"Email atau password salah.\"\n}"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Logout",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code 200', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response format sukses', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('success', true);",
									"    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('message');",
									"    pm.expect(json.message).to.include('Logout berhasil');",
									"});",
									"",
									"// Hapus token dari variable setelah logout",
									"pm.collectionVariables.set('token', '');",
									"console.log('Token dihapus setelah logout.');"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{token}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": ""
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/logout",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "logout"]
						},
						"description": "Logout dan mencabut token yang sedang digunakan.\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n    \"success\": true,\n    \"message\": \"Logout berhasil, token dicabut.\"\n}\n```"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Logout Berhasil",
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"success\": true,\n    \"message\": \"Logout berhasil, token dicabut.\"\n}"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "User",
			"description": "Endpoint terkait user yang sedang login.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Get Authenticated User",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code 200', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"// Jika 401, langsung skip assertion data (token belum terisi)",
									"if (pm.response.code === 401) {",
									"    console.warn('⚠️ 401 Unauthenticated — pastikan Login sudah dijalankan atau token valid.');",
									"    return;",
									"}",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response format konsisten (success, message, data)', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('success', true);",
									"    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('message', 'Data user.');",
									"    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('data');",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Data user di dalam .data memiliki field valid', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    var user = json.data;",
									"    pm.expect(user).to.have.property('id');",
									"    pm.expect(user).to.have.property('name');",
									"    pm.expect(user).to.have.property('email');",
									"    pm.expect(user).to.have.property('role');",
									"    pm.expect(user.role).to.match(/^(admin|mekanik)$/);",
									"    pm.expect(user).to.have.property('phone');",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Email valid', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json.data.email).to.match(/^[\\w.-]+@[\\w.-]+\\.\\w+$/);",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						},
